    "Description": "The mode of the CA.   All the device certificates that are registered using this CA will be registered in the same mode as the CA. For more information about certificate mode for device certificates, see [certificate mode](https://docs.aws.amazon.com/iot/latest/apireference/API_CertificateDescription.html#iot-Type-CertificateDescription-certificateMode).  Valid values are \"DEFAULT\" and \"SNI_ONLY\".",
